article.description: — Tahlik Chavez's 30 points led Louisiana Tech over Louisiana 72-67 on Saturday.
article.headline: Chavez's 30 lead Louisiana Tech over Louisiana 72-67
article.linkText: Chavez's 30 lead Louisiana Tech over Louisiana 72-67
article.story: RUSTON, La. -- — Tahlik Chavez's 30 points led Louisiana Tech over Louisiana 72-67 on Saturday. Chavez was 9 of 13 shooting, including 4 for 8 from 3-point range, and went 8 for 12 from the line for the Bulldogs (8-2). Daniel Batcho scored 14 points and added eight rebounds. Kobe Julien led the way for the Ragin' Cajuns (5-4) with 26 points, nine rebounds and two steals. Joe Charles added 10 points, three steals and two blocks for Louisiana. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
